@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@planIdFood = 11111111-1111-4111-a111-111111111101
@planIdChemical = 22222222-2222-4222-a222-222222222202
@planIdElectronics = 33333333-3333-4333-a333-333333333303
@planIdGeneral = 44444444-4444-4444-a444-444444444404
@planIdDangerousGoods = 55555555-5555-4555-a555-555555555505
@planIdChemicalDraft = 66666666-6666-4666-a666-666666666606
@planIdGeneralDraftMega = 77777777-7777-4777-a777-777777777707
@planIdAdrDraftReefer = 88888888-8888-4888-a888-888888888808
@unitIdFoodFinalizedFirst = 11111111-1111-4111-a111-000000000001
@unitIdChemicalDraftFirst = 66666666-6666-4666-a666-000000000001
@planIdNotExist = 00000000-dead-4bee-f000-000000000000
@unitIdNotExist = 00000000-dead-4bee-f000-000000000001

### Plan z żywnością (FOOD) – Reefer, jednostki jednorodne
GET {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{planIdFood}}
Accept: application/json

### Plan z chemią (CHEMICAL) – standard-curtainside, jednostki jednorodne
GET {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{planIdChemical}}
Accept: application/json

### Plan z elektroniką (ELECTRONICS) – Mega Trailer, jednostki jednorodne
GET {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{planIdElectronics}}
Accept: application/json

### Plan z towarem ogólnym (GENERAL) – Mega, jednostki jednorodne
GET {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{planIdGeneral}}
Accept: application/json

### Plan z towarem niebezpiecznym ADR – Reefer, jednostki jednorodne
GET {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{planIdDangerousGoods}}
Accept: application/json

### Opcjonalnie: weightUnit (domyślnie KG)
GET {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{planIdFood}}?weightUnit=LB
Accept: application/json

# ADD CARGO – walidacja reguł domenowych
# Uruchom 1–2 przed testami (tworzą plany DRAFT), potem 3–12 w kolejności.
# Wymagania cargo są teraz auto-derywowane z cargoType – nie trzeba ich wysyłać w payloadzie.
# Mapa: FOOD→isTemperatureControlled, ELECTRONICS+ADR→highSecurityRequired, reszta→brak specjalnych wymagań.




### 1. (EXPECTED SUCCESS) Create plan standard-curtainside – dla testów CHEMICAL, overweight, capabilities
# @name createPlanStandard
POST {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans
Content-Type: application/json

{ "trailerType": "standard-curtainside" }

### 2. (EXPECTED SUCCESS) Create plan reefer – dla testów FOOD+CHEMICAL coloading, too tall
# @name createPlanReefer
POST {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans
Content-Type: application/json

{ "trailerType": "reefer" }


### Plan 
GET {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{createPlanStandard.id}}
Accept: application/json

### 3. (EXPECTED SUCCESS) Dodaj CHEMICAL do planu z CHEMICAL (jednorodny, standard-curtainside)
# Wymaga: wcześniej uruchomione 1, plan ma 0 jednostek – dodajemy pierwszą
POST {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{createPlanStandard.id}}/cargo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "palletType": "cp1",
  "cargoType": "CHEMICAL",
  "weightKg": 500,
  "cargoHeightMm": 1200
}

### 4. (EXPECTED SUCCESS) Dodaj drugą paletę CHEMICAL do planu z CHEMICAL
POST {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{createPlanStandard.id}}/cargo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "palletType": "cp3",
  "cargoType": "CHEMICAL",
  "weightKg": 600,
  "cargoHeightMm": 1000
}

### 5. (EXPECTED SUCCESS) Dodaj FOOD do Reefer (pierwsza jednostka, przed testem coloading)
# FOOD auto-derywuje isTemperatureControlled: true → Reefer ma hasClimateControl: true → OK
POST {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{createPlanReefer.id}}/cargo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "palletType": "h1",
  "cargoType": "FOOD",
  "weightKg": 400,
  "cargoHeightMm": 1200
}

### 6. (EXPECTED FAIL) – Coloading: CHEMICAL do planu z FOOD (FOOD + CHEMICAL/ADR zabronione)
POST {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{createPlanReefer.id}}/cargo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "palletType": "cp1",
  "cargoType": "CHEMICAL",
  "weightKg": 500,
  "cargoHeightMm": 1200
}

### 7. (EXPECTED FAIL) – Nadwaga: paleta przekracza pojemność naczepy (standard 24t, Reefer 22t)
# Tworzymy nowy plan i dodajemy jedną gigantyczną paletę – epal1 max 4000kg per pallet
# Zamiast tego: dodaj 6×4000kg = 24t, potem 7. paleta → 28t > 24t
# Wymaga osobnego planu z 6 paletami. Użyjemy createPlanOverweight – najpierw go dodaj.
# @name createPlanOverweight
POST {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans
Content-Type: application/json

{ "trailerType": "standard-curtainside" }

### 8a–8f. (EXPECTED FAIL) Dodaj 6 palet po 4000kg (epal1 max) = 24t dokładnie
# @name addOverweight1
POST {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{createPlanOverweight.id}}/cargo
Content-Type: application/json

{"palletType":"epal1","cargoType":"GENERAL","weightKg":4000,"cargoHeightMm":1000}

### 8b
POST {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{createPlanOverweight.id}}/cargo
Content-Type: application/json

{"palletType":"epal1","cargoType":"GENERAL","weightKg":4000,"cargoHeightMm":1000}

### 8c
POST {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{createPlanOverweight.id}}/cargo
Content-Type: application/json

{"palletType":"epal1","cargoType":"GENERAL","weightKg":4000,"cargoHeightMm":1000}

### 8d
POST {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{createPlanOverweight.id}}/cargo
Content-Type: application/json

{"palletType":"epal1","cargoType":"GENERAL","weightKg":4000,"cargoHeightMm":1000}

### 8e
POST {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{createPlanOverweight.id}}/cargo
Content-Type: application/json

{"palletType":"epal1","cargoType":"GENERAL","weightKg":4000,"cargoHeightMm":1000}

### 8f
POST {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{createPlanOverweight.id}}/cargo
Content-Type: application/json

{"palletType":"epal1","cargoType":"GENERAL","weightKg":4000,"cargoHeightMm":1000}

### 9. (EXPECTED FAIL) – Nadwaga: 7. paleta → 28t > max 24t
POST {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{createPlanOverweight.id}}/cargo
Content-Type: application/json

{"palletType":"epal1","cargoType":"GENERAL","weightKg":4000,"cargoHeightMm":1000}

### 10. (EXPECTED FAIL) – Paleta za wysoka dla Reefer (2600mm). EPAL1: 144 + 2500 = 2644mm > 2600mm
# @name createPlanTall
POST {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans
Content-Type: application/json

{ "trailerType": "reefer" }

### 11. (EXPECTED FAIL) – cargoHeightMm 2500 → totalHeight 2644 > 2600
POST {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{createPlanTall.id}}/cargo
Content-Type: application/json

{"palletType":"epal1","cargoType":"GENERAL","weightKg":500,"cargoHeightMm":2500}

### 12. (EXPECTED FAIL) – Trailer bez klimatyzacji: FOOD wymaga isTemperatureControlled, standard-curtainside nie ma
# @name createPlanNoClimate
POST {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans
Content-Type: application/json

{ "trailerType": "standard-curtainside" }

### 13. (EXPECTED FAIL) – FOOD auto-derywuje isTemperatureControlled: true → standard-curtainside nie ma hasClimateControl
POST {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{createPlanNoClimate.id}}/cargo
Content-Type: application/json

{"palletType":"h1","cargoType":"FOOD","weightKg":400,"cargoHeightMm":1200}

### 14. (EXPECTED FAIL) – highSecurityRequired: ADR/ELECTRONICS auto-derywuje highSecurityRequired: true → standard-curtainside nie ma hasHighSecurityLock
POST {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{createPlanStandard.id}}/cargo
Content-Type: application/json

{"palletType":"cp1","cargoType":"ADR","weightKg":500,"cargoHeightMm":1200}

### 15. (EXPECTED FAIL) – Plan już sfinalizowany (11111111 = FOOD, FINALIZED)
POST {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{planIdFood}}/cargo
Content-Type: application/json

{"palletType":"h1","cargoType":"FOOD","weightKg":400,"cargoHeightMm":1200}



# REMOVE CARGO – DELETE /cargo-plans/{id}/cargo/{unitId}
# Usuwa konkretną paletę z planu wg jej UUID. Plan musi być w statusie DRAFT.
# Dane z seed: planIdChemicalDraft (66666666, standard-curtainside, DRAFT), unitIdChemicalDraftFirst

### 16. (EXPECTED SUCCESS) Usuń jednostkę CHEMICAL z planu DRAFT
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{planIdChemicalDraft}}/cargo/{{unitIdChemicalDraftFirst}}

### 17. (EXPECTED FAIL) – Plan nie istnieje (404)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{planIdNotExist}}/cargo/{{unitIdChemicalDraftFirst}}

### 18. (EXPECTED FAIL) – Jednostka o podanym ID nie należy do planu (400)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{planIdChemicalDraft}}/cargo/{{unitIdNotExist}}

### 19. (EXPECTED FAIL) – Plan jest już sfinalizowany, usuwanie zabronione (400)
# planIdFood = 11111111 (FINALIZED), unitIdFoodFinalizedFirst to jedna z jego palet
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{planIdFood}}/cargo/{{unitIdFoodFinalizedFirst}}





# CHANGE TRAILER – PUT /cargo-plans/{id}/trailer
# Podmienia naczepę w planie DRAFT. Po zmianie wszystkie przypisane jednostki są
# re-walidowane pod kątem możliwości nowej naczepy i jej pojemności.
# Dane z seed: planIdGeneralDraftMega (77777777, mega, DRAFT) i planIdAdrDraftReefer (88888888, reefer, DRAFT)

### 20. (EXPECTED SUCCESS) Zmień naczepę z mega na standard-curtainside (GENERAL – brak specjalnych wymagań)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{planIdGeneralDraftMega}}/trailer
Content-Type: application/json

{"trailerType": "standard-curtainside"}

### 21. (EXPECTED FAIL) – Nieprawidłowy typ naczepy (400)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{planIdGeneralDraftMega}}/trailer
Content-Type: application/json

{"trailerType": "flatbed"}

### 22. (EXPECTED FAIL) – Re-walidacja: ładunek ADR wymaga highSecurityLock, standard-curtainside go nie ma (400)
# planIdAdrDraftReefer (88888888, reefer, DRAFT) ma palety ADR (highSecurityRequired=true)
# standard-curtainside ma hasHighSecurityLock: false → re-walidacja odrzuca
PUT {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{planIdAdrDraftReefer}}/trailer
Content-Type: application/json

{"trailerType": "standard-curtainside"}

### 23. (EXPECTED FAIL) – Plan nie istnieje (404)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{planIdNotExist}}/trailer
Content-Type: application/json

{"trailerType": "mega"}

### 24. (EXPECTED FAIL) – Plan sfinalizowany, zmiana naczepy zabroniona (400)
# planIdChemical = 22222222 (FINALIZED)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{planIdChemical}}/trailer
Content-Type: application/json

{"trailerType": "mega"}



# FINALIZE – POST /cargo-plans/{id}/finalize
# Oznacza plan jako FINALIZED – blokuje dalsze modyfikacje.
# Warunek: plan musi mieć co najmniej jedną jednostkę i nie może przekraczać pojemności.

### 25. (setup) Utwórz plan do finalizacji
# @name createPlanToFinalize
POST {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans
Content-Type: application/json

{"trailerType": "mega"}

### 26. (setup) Dodaj jednostkę do planu przed finalizacją
POST {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{createPlanToFinalize.id}}/cargo
Content-Type: application/json

{"palletType":"epal1","cargoType":"GENERAL","weightKg":500,"cargoHeightMm":1000}

### 27. (EXPECTED SUCCESS) Finalizuj plan z ładunkiem – status zmienia się na FINALIZED
POST {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{createPlanToFinalize.id}}/finalize





### 28. (setup) Utwórz pusty plan do testu błędu finalizacji
# @name createEmptyPlanToFinalize
POST {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans
Content-Type: application/json

{"trailerType": "standard-curtainside"}

### 29. (EXPECTED FAIL) – Nie można sfinalizować pustego planu (brak jednostek) (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{createEmptyPlanToFinalize.id}}/finalize

### 30. (EXPECTED FAIL) – Plan już sfinalizowany, powtórna finalizacja zabroniona (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{createPlanToFinalize.id}}/finalize

### 31. (EXPECTED FAIL) – Plan nie istnieje (404)
POST {{baseUrl}}/cargo-plans/{{planIdNotExist}}/finalize
